function_call.name: get_risks
function_call.arguments: {"risks":[{"Description":"Insect-borne diseases like malaria, HAT, leishmaniasis, LF, and onchocerciasis may spread due to ineffective vector control methods.","Impact":"Increased morbidity and mortality due to the spread of these diseases.","Mitigation":"Implementation of effective and sustainable vector control methods, such as eave tubes, eave closure, and window screening.","Technologies":"Eave tubes, insecticide-treated netting, effective vector control strategies.","People":"Populations at risk of insect-borne diseases in areas with high disease burden.","Owner":"Health organizations, government agencies, local communities."}]}
